s://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/f9/35/da/f935da83-2982-8390-1de8-ee9e8e1255dc/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","averageUserRating":4.5,"trackCensoredName":"UT.no","trackViewUrl":"https://apps.apple.com/no/app/ut-no/id510575024?uo=4","contentAdvisoryRating":"4+","minimumOsVersion":"15.1","artistId":922601500,"artistName":"Den Norske Turistforening","price":0.0,"bundleId":"no.nrk.mobil.UT","isVppDeviceBasedLicensingEnabled":true,"trackId":510575024,"trackName":"UT.no","releaseDate":"2012-04-03T21:45:55Z","genreIds":["6003","6010"],"sellerName":"Den Norske Turistforening","primaryGenreName":"Travel","primaryGenreId":6003,"releaseNotes":"A new and improved version of the UT app is here! We’ve worked to make the app easier to use, expanded its functionality, and improved offline support so it works better when you’re out exploring without mobile coverage.\n\nHighlights in this update:\n\n- The app automatically downloads data and content so it’s available when you’re on a trip without mobile coverage\n- Updated design, user interface, and navigation\n- New and improved map functionality\n- A new and more stable solution for downloading offline maps\n- Track your trips\n- Save your own favorite places\n- A dedicated page for CheckUT\n- English language support for app features\n\nNote: If you've downloaded offline maps in earlier versions of the app, you will unfortunately need to download them again.\n\nRead more about what’s new or changed: https://hjelp.ut.no/hc/no/articles/27815038210834","currentVersionReleaseDate":"2026-03-13T06:04:56Z","version":"6.0.3","wrapperType":"software","currency":"NOK","description":"With the UT app you can:\n\n- View detailed hiking maps with marked trails or ski tracks, as well as other useful map layers for trip planning\n- Find thousands of trip suggestions, cabins, and destinasjons all over the country\n- Save your favorite trips or cabins in your own lists\n- Get inspired by our lists of recommended destinations, cabins, and trips\n- “Check in” at cabins and destinations with SjekkUT\n- Track your trips and save your own favorite places\n- Download offline maps that you can use when you’re outdoors without mobile coverage\n\t\nRemember that all activities in nature is at your own risk, and the app is only intended as a extra tool for planning and navigation. Your phone may run out of battery or stop working. Therefore, bring a map and compass when going on a trip in the outdoors - they always work. Also see the Norwegian Mountain Code at https://www.dnt.no/en/mountaincode. These tips helps you plan and complete a safe, enjoyable trip – which is also safe.","fileSizeBytes":"113517568","formattedPrice":"Free","trackContentRating":"4+","userRatingCountForCurrentVersion":2,"averageUserRatingForCurrentVersion":4.5,"sellerUrl":"https://ut.no/","languageCodesISO2A":["EN"],"genres":["Travel","Navigation"],"userRatingCount":2}